      "description": "padding(union[int,tuple]) – The padding size to pad the input tensor.\nIf padding is an integer: all directions will be padded with the same size.\nIf padding is a tuple: uses\\((pad\\_left, pad\\_right, pad\\_up, pad\\_down)\\)to pad."
